extends layout.pug

block content
  main
    section.search-page
      .search-page__wrapper(class=!searchList.length ? 'search-page__wrapper--empty' : '')
        h1 Поиск
        .search.search-page__form
          form(action='/search/results', method='get')
            label
              input(type='text', name="query", placeholder='Что ищем?', value=searchWord)
            button.search__button.button.button--transparent(type='submit') Найти
          each searchElem in searchList
            .search__result
              time.search__date(datetime='2019-03-21T20:33')=searchElem.createdDate
              a(href="/articles/" + searchElem.id).search__link=searchElem.title
        if !searchList.length
          p.search-page__empty
            | Ничего не нашлось
